# RavenStack SaaS Analytics Dashboard

An end-to-end data analytics project that analyzes customer behavior, subscription revenue, support performance, feature usage, and customer churn for a fictional SaaS company, **RavenStack**.

This project demonstrates the complete analytics workflow—from building a PostgreSQL database and writing SQL queries to preparing data with Python and creating interactive Power BI dashboards.

---

## Project Overview

The objective of this project is to transform raw SaaS business data into meaningful business insights.

The analysis focuses on:

- Customer growth
- Monthly & Annual Recurring Revenue (MRR & ARR)
- Customer churn
- Customer acquisition channels
- Product feature usage
- Support performance

The final deliverable is an interactive Power BI report designed for business stakeholders.

---

## Tech Stack

- **PostgreSQL** – Database Management
- **SQL** – Data Validation & Business Analysis
- **Python (Pandas)** – Data Preparation
- **Power BI** – Interactive Dashboards
- **Git & GitHub** – Version Control

---

